      "content": "2 units sounds okay i guess. but i also had a small snack like 45 mins ago, so the insulin might overlap with that. if i take the 2 units now, how long should i wait before checking again to make sure i dont crash? also i feel a bit shaky, should i just take the insulin and push through it?",
