      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait ibuprofen for shakiness? i thought that was for pain. i'm actually feeling a bit sweaty and lightheaded now, like my heart is racing a little. if i take the 2 units like u suggested, will that help stabilize me or make the shakiness worse? just tell me what i should do right now to fix this quickly so i can get to my meeting.",
